des:
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo after connecting Alexa to your Fansio products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our "Fansio" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Create a new account for your "Fansio" app;
(3). You need to have a Fansio devices installed to your fan;
(4). Configure the device in our "Fansio" app and add a name for your device which will be used in "Fansio" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Fansio" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill for "Fansio", and you'll be navigated to the Fansio login page;
(9). Input your Fansio account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Setup is complete.

You can enjoy voice control on your ceiling fan like:
Alexa, turn on the light
Alexa, turn off the light
Alexa, set light to 50 percent
Alexa, dim light to 10 percent
Alexa, turn fan on
Alexa, turn fan off
